==English==

===Noun===

'''epifauna''' (''plural'' '''epifaunae''' or '''epifaunas''')

# A [[fauna]] characterized by members whose typical [[life site]]s are on the [[outer]] [[surface]] of their [[environment]], as opposed to [[within]] it, e.g. [[animals]] living on top of the [[sediment]] at the [[seafloor]].

